<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/user/user_service/style_no-pillbox.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>


    <% if (user && user.role === 'S') { %>
    <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_senior') %>
<% } else { %>
      <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_about') %>
<% } %>

  <main class="nopill-main">
    <div class="nopill-card">

      <div class="nopill-icon">
        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M10 7V5a2 2 0 014 0v2"/>
          <line x1="9" y1="14" x2="15" y2="14" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="nopill-card__title">약통번호를 등록해주세요!</h1>
      <p class="nopill-card__desc">
        대시보드를 이용하려면 먼저 스마트 약상자를 등록해야 합니다.<br>
        약상자 하단의 시리얼 번호를 확인 후 등록해 주세요.
      </p>

      <a href="/user/user_service/register-pillbox" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px;" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M10 7V5a2 2 0 014 0v2"/>
          <path d="M12 12v4M10 14h4"/>
        </svg>
        약통 등록하러 가기
      </a>

      <a href="/user/user_service/about" class="nopill-card__link">약통 구매가 필요하신가요? →</a>

    </div>
  </main>

<footer class="footer">
  © 2026 <span>약속:藥束</span> | Team Jetson5 | 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼
</footer>

</body>
</html>